#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_worldmarginshape.rst:19
msgid ""
"An infinite plane shape for 3D collisions. Note that the :ref:`Plane "
"<class_Plane>`'s normal matters; anything \"below\" the plane will "
"collide with it. If the ``WorldMarginShape`` is used in a "
":ref:`PhysicsBody <class_PhysicsBody>`, it will cause colliding objects "
"placed \"below\" it to teleport \"above\" the plane."
msgstr ""

